steps.name: When User clicks on the Admin tab from the menu
And Admin panel page should display Admin / User Management options
When User clicks on the add button
And User enters employee name "Radha Gupta"
And User clicks on the save button
Then The system should show a success message "Successfully Saved"
And The new user "Radha Gupta" should appear in the user list
